news_header: Some products may be scarce due to upcoming strikes, but overall purchasing behavior remains unchanged, according to the head of S-Group's grocery store. Customers are buying more food in preparation for the strikes, while some believe stores will remain well-stocked.
news_original_title: Kaupan lakko sai osan suomalaisista varautumaan, ja hyllyjäkin tyhjeni – ”Ostin kyllä hieman enemmän”
news_text: The strikes will affect logistics and store operations starting next week, with around 70,000 employees participating.
